#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/editing/introduction.rst:349
msgid ""
"This sets the :doc:`Soft Body Goal Weight "
"</modeling/curves/properties/introduction>` of selected control points. "
"The precise value can be adjusted in the Operator Panel. To adjust the "
"*Mean Weight* (average) of selected control points use "
":menuselection:`Properties region --> Transform --> Mean Weight`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/editing/introduction.rst:356
msgid "Smooth"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/editing/introduction.rst:362
msgid ":menuselection:`Tool Shelf --> Tools --> Curve Tools --> Modeling: Smooth`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/editing/introduction.rst:363
msgid ":menuselection:`Specials --> Smooth`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/editing/introduction.rst:365
msgid ""
"Curve smoothing is available through the specials menu. For Bézier "
"curves, this smoothing operation reduces the distance between the "
"selected control point/s and their neighbors, while keeping the neighbors"
" anchored. Does not effect control point tangents."
msgstr ""
"le lissage (smoothing) de courge est disponible via le menu *specials*. "
"Pour les courbes de Bézier, cette opération de lissage réduit la distance"
" entre les points de contrôle sélectionnés et leurs voisins, tout en "
"gardant les voisins ancrés. N'affecte pas les tangentes des points de "
"contrôle."

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/editing/introduction.rst:372
msgid "Original, unsmoothed Curve."
msgstr "Courbe d'origine, non lissée."

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/editing/introduction.rst:376
msgid ""
"Entire curve smoothed over 20 times by holding :kbd:`Shift-R` to repeat "
"last step."
msgstr ""
"Courbe entière lissée plus de 20 fois en tenant :kbd:`Maj-R` pour répéter"
" la dernière étape."

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/editing/introduction.rst:380
msgid "Only three control points in the center smoothed over 20 times."
msgstr "Seulement trois points de contrôle au centre, lissé plus de 20 fois."

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/editing/introduction.rst:384
msgid "Hooks"
msgstr ""

